    ('Druid (Circle of the Sea): Aquatic Affinity', 'Your Wrath of the Sea Emanation grows to 10 feet, and you gain a Swim Speed equal to your Speed.'),
    ('Druid (Circle of the Sea): Circle of the Sea Spells', 'Always prepare Fog Cloud, Gust of Wind, Ray of Frost, Shatter, and Thunderwave; later add Lightning Bolt, Water Breathing, Control Water, Ice Storm, Conjure Elemental, and Hold Monster.'),
    ('Druid (Circle of the Sea): Oceanic Gift', 'You can manifest Wrath of the Sea around a willing creature within 60 feet, or around both that creature and yourself by expending two Wild Shape uses.'),
    ('Druid (Circle of the Sea): Stormborn', 'While Wrath of the Sea is active, you gain a Fly Speed equal to your Speed and Resistance to Cold, Lightning, and Thunder damage.'),
