    ('Druid (Circle of the Stars): Starry Form: Dragon Flight', 'Your Dragon constellation grants flight while active.'),
    ('Druid (Circle of the Stars): Twinkling Constellations', 'Your Starry Form improves: Archer and Chalice use 2d8, Dragon gains a 20-foot Fly Speed with hover, and you can change constellation at the start of each turn.'),
    ('Druid: Archdruid', 'Regain one Wild Shape use when rolling Initiative with none left, convert Wild Shape uses into a spell slot once per Long Rest, and age more slowly.'),
    ('Druid: Beast Spells', 'While in Wild Shape, you can cast spells except those with costly or consumed Material components.'),
    ('Druid: Druidic', 'You know Druidic and always have Speak with Animals prepared. You can also leave hidden messages that other Druidic speakers automatically understand.'),
    ('Druid: Elemental Fury', 'Choose Potent Spellcasting to add Wisdom to Druid cantrip damage, or Primal Strike to add 1d8 Cold, Fire, Lightning, or Thunder damage to a weapon or Wild Shape attack once per turn.'),
    ('Druid: Epic Boon', 'You gain an Epic Boon feat or another feat for which you qualify.'),
    ('Druid: Improved Elemental Fury', 'Your Elemental Fury choice improves: Potent Spellcasting increases long-range Druid cantrip range, or Primal Strike deals 2d8 extra damage.'),
    ('Druid: Primal Order', 'Choose Magician for one extra Druid cantrip and a Wisdom-based bonus to Arcana or Nature checks, or Warden for Martial weapons and Medium armor.'),
    ('Druid: Spellcasting', 'Cast prepared Druid spells using Wisdom. You start with two Druid cantrips and four level 1 prepared spells, and use a Druidic Focus as a spellcasting focus.'),
    ('Druid: Wild Companion', 'Magic Action to expend a spell slot or a Wild Shape use to cast Find Familiar without Material components; the familiar is Fey and disappears after your next Long Rest.'),
    ('Druid: Wild Resurgence', 'Once on each of your turns, if you have no Wild Shape uses left, you can expend a spell slot to regain one use. Once per Long Rest, expend one Wild Shape use to regain a level 1 spell slot.'),
    ('Druid: Wild Shape', 'Bonus Action to assume a known Beast form for hours equal to half your Druid level. Gain Temporary Hit Points equal to your Druid level and use known forms by level.'),
    ('Fighter (Battle Master): Combat Superiority', 'Learn three maneuvers fueled by four d8 Superiority Dice. Gain more maneuvers and dice at higher Fighter levels, and regain dice on Short or Long Rest.'),
