    ('Fighter (Champion): Additional Fighting Style', 'Gain another Fighting Style feat of your choice.'),
    ('Fighter (Champion): Heroic Warrior', 'During combat, if you start your turn without Heroic Inspiration, you can give yourself Heroic Inspiration.'),
