    ('Fighter (Champion): Superior Critical', 'Your attack rolls with weapons and Unarmed Strikes score a Critical Hit on a d20 roll of 18-20.'),
    ('Fighter (Champion): Survivor Rally', 'Gain Advantage on Death Saving Throws, treat 18-20 as a 20 on those saves, and regain HP at the start of your turns while Bloodied and above 0 HP.'),
    ('Fighter (Eldritch Knight): Arcane Charge', 'When you use your Action Surge, you can teleport up to 30ft to an unoccupied space you can see.'),
