    ('Fighter (Psi Warrior): Bulwark of Force', 'Bonus Action to grant yourself and allies Half Cover for 1 minute.'),
    ('Fighter (Psi Warrior): Guarded Mind', 'Gain resistance to Psychic damage. If Frightened or Charmed, spend a Psi die to end the effect.'),
