    ('Fighter: Epic Boon', 'You gain an Epic Boon feat or another feat for which you qualify.'),
    ('Fighter: Extra Attack', 'You can attack twice instead of once whenever you take the Attack action.'),
    ('Fighter: Fighting Style', 'Gain a Fighting Style feat of your choice. Whenever you gain a Fighter level, you can replace it with another Fighting Style feat.'),
    ('Fighter: Indomitable', 'When you fail a saving throw, reroll it with a bonus equal to your Fighter level. Uses increase at higher Fighter levels.'),
    ('Fighter: Second Wind', 'Bonus Action to regain HP equal to 1d10 + your Fighter level. Uses recover on Short and Long Rests and increase at higher Fighter levels.'),
    ('Fighter: Studied Attacks', 'When you miss a creature with an attack roll, you have Advantage on your next attack roll against that creature.'),
    ('Fighter: Tactical Master', 'When you attack with a weapon whose mastery property you can use, you can replace that property with Push, Sap, or Slow for that attack.'),
    ('Fighter: Tactical Mind', 'When you fail an ability check, expend Second Wind to add 1d10 to the roll. If the check still fails, the Second Wind use is not spent.'),
